;(First interaction)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 504052001: Config/Level/Mission/5040520/Act/Act504052001.json-->
::'''Magdalena:''' Ah, what a splendid day indeed... Are you here to visit? You're a tad late, unfortunately.
::'''Magdalena:''' The last of the sweet treats has just been given away. Had you arrived a moment sooner, you could have snagged the final batch.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Are you the temple's chef?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504052004-->
:::'''Magdalena:''' No, I'm merely a humble maid, though I've had the privilege of serving the Holy Maiden. I've undertaken various tasks here in the temple &mdash; sweeping, laundry, assisting in sacred rituals...
:::'''Magdalena:''' But what I love most is baking. There's something about a sweet that can brighten a gloomy day. Amid all the grave responsibilities in the temple, it's these little joys that I hold dear.
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504052011-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504052011-->
:::'''Magdalena:''' I still recall how the Holy Maiden once savored these desserts, calling them "heartwarming."
:::'''Magdalena:''' Years have flown by, but it feels like it all happened just yesterday. Time does fly...
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Have you been working here long?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504052014-->
::::'''Magdalena:''' Indeed. I was sent here to aid the Holy Maiden since I was old enough to walk. I've spent decades within these walls.
::::'''Magdalena:''' I had sleek, jet-black hair and not a wrinkle in sight back then. Quite a different story from today.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} ...I am hungry now.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504052017-->
::::'''Magdalena:''' Ha, perhaps it's the remnant scents of today's baking. I only use the finest ingredients, after all.
::::'''Magdalena:''' Every morning, I wake early to sift the finest flour and strain the purest honey. The sweet aroma is so tempting, even I can't help but start to drool.
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504052019-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504052019-->
:::'''Magdalena:''' Over the years, I've seen many come to seek the Titans' prophecy or search for something profound within these temple walls.
:::'''Magdalena:''' But some might just need a place to think or a listening ear... Everyone has their own tale to tell.
:::'''Magdalena:''' {{MC|f=My girl|m=My boy}}, though your quest is unknown to me, feel free to stop by anytime for a chat over hot tea and treats. You might just find what you're looking for.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Is there something special about this dessert?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504052007-->
:::'''Magdalena:''' It's my secret recipe, cherished by all in the temple for years. Every time I open the oven, the aroma alone draws a crowd, all eager for a taste.
:::'''Magdalena:''' The funny thing is, after all these years serving in the temple, people remember not so much me, but more so the sweet treats I bake.
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504052011-->
