:::{{DIcon|Talk}} Can you show me how to make these sweet treats?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504052113-->
::::'''Magdalena:''' Ah, finally someone wants to learn this! Everyone just loves eating, but no one wants to bother making it. It's quite simple &mdash; you just need to put in some effort. Come on. I'll teach you, so pay attention.
::::'''Magdalena:''' First, sift the flour well and choose only the purest honey. Then, you need to put your heart into the process of baking. It's crucial to tailor the dough to suit individual tastes and to get the baking just right.
::::'''Magdalena:''' Most importantly, when baking, always offer a prayer to the Titans, blessing those who will enjoy your treats. Skipping this step means they just won't taste as delightful.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} Did you serve the Holy Maiden once?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504052117-->
::::'''Magdalena:''' Yes, I once served as a maid for a previous Holy Maiden. Despite her title, she was just a young girl. She'd even sneak a piece of dessert away while having snacks, and when I asked her why, she said she wanted to save it to share with me later.
::::'''Magdalena:''' Her gaze always made my heart melt. Even though I had no children of my own at that time... *cough* It may sound sacrilegious, but I felt as if she were no different from a daughter to me.
::::'''Magdalena:''' But let's keep this conversation between us. It wouldn't be right to spread such personal reflections.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} What do you normally do around the temple?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504052121-->
::::'''Magdalena:''' What else can I do? My days are filled with simple, essential chores.
::::'''Magdalena:''' Cleaning the temple, then prepare treats. Sometimes the young priests seek wisdom from us elders. When it's quiet, I just sit here, offering tea to those who pass by.
::::'''Magdalena:''' Life might be simple, but it's fulfilling. This temple is my home.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Exit}} I don't have much else to say.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504052125-->
::::'''Magdalena:''' No worries. You carry on with your day. It's rare these days for anyone to care for an old lady's stories.
::::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::{{DIcon|Exit}} It's okay. I just came to check on you.
:::'''Magdalena:''' Ah, you're too kind. If you ever need a break, feel free to come over and talk to me anytime.
:::'''Magdalena:''' May the Titans bless you, youngster... and all those who wander in search of clarity.
